dct_title_s: Souvenir map of prominent motion picture stars homes
dct_description_sm: Includes names of stars and their addresses with about half of them marked on the Beverly Hills area map. Includes indexes to celebrity addresses. "Compliments of the Beverly Hills U S O." Originally issued folded to 22 x 13 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: [Beverly Hills, Calif.? : Beverly Hills U.S.O.?, ca. 1940-1945]
